{"tid":222654,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人需唔需要信仰","createTime":"2017-04-29T16:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T16:27:17.000Z","uid":60423,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0119766c9fb451026f87e3383dbc74a0a283fa5","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"唔好屌耶撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n信仰唔一定指宗教，其實簡單至及時行樂都可以<br />\n大家會唔會覺得如果冇信仰嘅話，人就變得好冇自己嘅方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你會話如果人人都有信仰，咁總有人有一樣信仰，咁佢地嘅人生方向咪大同小異，都一樣冇意思活唔出真正自己，所以唔應該有信仰限住自己<br />\n拿，但係有信仰又唔一定係要跟曬，只係俾我一個我想活出我人生嘅方向<br />\n我都知講到1999，因為我自己都唔知自己覺得邊邊啱<br />\n只係想問問，屎儈啲咁諗，會唔會有信仰好過冇信仰。<br />\n同個痴線佬傾完計想問問巴打們嘅睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然都可以講下耶撚依啲宗教信仰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f1340685cb776d5c6e19dc8c7229e433b2846c","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮=要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮=唔一定洗<br />\n補充:無神論好似都係一種信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731d68c1edeaf4be90776f3ffdb6513bfa97d786","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"利申負皮"},{"pid":"1c23ab8fb64fe1a5f5e43f9390fe3f3cf9601005","tid":222654,"uid":79709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"要，但我冇 所以依家日日成碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fd79b0750173f0e6f501df1275d9c1550eb3b7","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要，但我冇 所以依家日日成碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要呢巴打做乜覺得自己成碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你覺得有咩信仰又點幫到你<br />\n你想有信仰就即刻可以有架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37429f7610c0a79488b4cffdbb3b2eaf530748ab","tid":222654,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"我只信科學 其他垃圾教死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c47d2cb8b491e1348e5937fd0642ba278cf17c8","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只信科學 其他垃圾教死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我話信科學都係一種信仰你又點睇<br />\n又或者唔一定係乜乜教(我都好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n好on9咁邪不能勝正都可以係你嘅信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或有冇巴打覺得我對信仰嘅定義錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea1ad5a7c1b5af657bf17c6ec44b4e98eb76ce2","tid":222654,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我只信科學 其他垃圾教死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信科學都係一種信仰嚟"},{"pid":"43bb486756a335557338d43129d8b1a90c4b4f5c","tid":222654,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T17:49:29.000Z","msg":"你講嘅似係信念多過信仰wor...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862b5bf15cbb34e0116155a9667230e88b574b93","tid":222654,"uid":89851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:46:53.000Z","msg":"及時行樂都算嘅話<br />\n樓主你意思係咪座右銘或者做人嘅宗旨之類？"},{"pid":"7ad697da45e5dbae2d3650735304528d6397f4c3","tid":222654,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我只信科學 其他垃圾教死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信科學都係一種信仰嚟</blockquote><br />\n不如你定義左咩係信仰先討論落去"},{"pid":"f8d3aa821e8f3b3e65bb2dcbe0192700e48477f3","tid":222654,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T18:53:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5011dbfaf89d8c429612774c973dc45c80e5325","tid":222654,"uid":70561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T19:29:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60807a2f9aae7171e2b006907d1d87929eeb773c","tid":222654,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:21:23.000Z","msg":"留名學野 希望有高質意見"},{"pid":"448730316440be543d37529f124ea134d3d73c38","tid":222654,"uid":34093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:23:34.000Z","msg":"其實信仰同方向有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">btw, 我信眼見 同 科學</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa33446895a82d66166757f43bcbf528c2e615ba","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講嘅似係信念多過信仰wor...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打覺得個分別係點<br />\n其實我開post係想問下大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己都好亂唔知講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b0c54ebbb5c8ec75eb19eb6815dab9c8d680a5","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>及時行樂都算嘅話<br />\n樓主你意思係咪座右銘或者做人嘅宗旨之類？</blockquote><br />\n你覺得座右銘或者做人嘅宗旨可唔可以都成為人嘅信仰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔得嘅話點去分兩者<br />\n信仰一定唔只宗教，但又去到咩程度都算係信仰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依個係我第一個諗唔明嘅問題"},{"pid":"ba4f22f521e852b0a2e1e6e6f56e7a4c3f7b3d49","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我只信科學 其他垃圾教死撚開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信科學都係一種信仰嚟</blockquote><br />\n不如你定義左咩係信仰先討論落去</blockquote><br />\n其實個定義係咩我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗係可以大家討論一個共同定義<br />\n上網搵過下都唔太知講緊乜好模糊"},{"pid":"7b3b8f75e31588103290092f79940b80aaf4fa6b","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T22:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>需要，人總有軟弱時</blockquote><br />\n咁信仰係咪唯一途徑解決問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78344acd03db70d842496d20825821b76e57ed1b","tid":222654,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:01:29.000Z","msg":"冇神既宗教算唔算信仰<br />\n<br />\n佛教唔係宗教係純信仰"},{"pid":"7a2a5d6a5e0a3e69b0ab59dc300dd08edaec68ab","tid":222654,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:02:27.000Z","msg":"無信仰點控制蠢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2088b67ec52a9936dbb1013ec76a9de6b2113515","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:03:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實信仰同方向有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">btw, 我信眼見 同 科學</span></span></blockquote><br />\n你咁問得一定係有啲睇法關於兩者不如講多啲出黎，點解佢地有/冇關係/無必然關係<br />\n我都信科學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但俾個癲佬搞到好亂諗多左信仰嘅野"},{"pid":"f5368e5e84b56d79cfb26f8c1a3b13a553b2bda4","tid":222654,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:03:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得信仰係對管治有一定幫助, 大部份宗教都係叫人向善, 又可以產生不少經濟活動<br />\n<br />\n但從個人角度, 宗教係多餘,  宗教會令部份人失去(局限)自由意志而自己唔覺, 與其信關公,耶耶, 觀音, 不如自己相信自己, 行自己嘅路"},{"pid":"f9d9069cbc7d1b1194cd62f09196db43b0ceacad","tid":222654,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇神既宗教算唔算信仰<br />\n<br />\n佛教唔係宗教係純信仰</blockquote><br />\n我覺得宗教只係信仰入面嘅一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0596cc9b4e04102f786c43a94a027ff97ecf190","tid":222654,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T23:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇神既宗教算唔算信仰<br />\n<br />\n佛教唔係宗教係純信仰</blockquote><br />\n我覺得宗教只係信仰入面嘅一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nok good we cld talk"}]}